                </div><!-- end article top div --><div class="clear" style="width:0;"></div><div class="article-auth"><div class="auth-author" style="float:left;">By <a href="/authors/zeke_miller/">Zeke Miller</a>, <a href="/authors/alan_suderman/">Alan Suderman</a> & <a href="/authors/kevin_freking/">Kevin Freking</a></div><span class="auth-date" style="float:right;">April 17, 2020</span></div><div class="article-body"><div class="alpha"><span class="section-border"></span><!-- sphereit start --><!-- startprint --><div class="article-top hide-module"><div class="article-title-wrapper">
                                <div class="article-title"><h1>Trump Unveils Road Map for Reopening Schools, Businesses in 3 Phases</h1></div></div></div><!-- end article top div --><div class="mobile-social-bar">
